    "description": "Newton the kitten is a tourist and very curious kitten<br><br>He went to travel with his owner to an island for a vacation, but when it was time to leave Newton went to discover new things on the island and got lost!<br><br>His owner is waiting for him at the kiosk so he can catch the plane and leave, but Newton doesn't know the way to get home<br><br>Newton is lost on the island, only you can help him!<br><br>You need to unscramble the hexagonal tiles to form a path where Newton will be able to reach his owner<br><br>Your challenge is to connect all the tiles with food so that Newton the kitten can reach its owner without hunger, otherwise Newton will die of hunger on the way<br><br>Rivers, mountains and bridges will challenge you to find the best way<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cats and Puzzle: A cute and pleasant experience<br></li><li>Rotate the camera freely with the right mouse button<br></li><li>52 uniquely assembled levels<br></li><li>5 island themes with many additional mechanics<br></li><li>Original music and effects<br></li><li>Configure graphics for your computer<br></li><li>Steam Cloud and Steam Achievements</li></ul>",
